videos.description: Murray State's Ja Morant assists on two dunks and then gets a fast-break layup of his own.

videos.headline: Morant scores and assists for a quick 6 points

videos.description: Ja Morant calls for an iso and takes the ball through the paint for a last-second bucket to give Murray State a 40-35 lead at the half.

videos.headline: Morant unstoppable on layup to end first half

videos.description: Ja Morant jumps up to draw the foul and hits the shot while falling down to finish the and-1 play.
videos.headline: Morant hits and-1 jumper

videos.description: Ja Morant comes over to help on defense and not only gets way up to block the shot, but also comes down with the rebound.
